Description_lang: Transforms you into an agent of Orix the All-Seer, suffering $s1% of maximum health as Shadow damage and disguising you as an eredar.Agents of Orix can loot Intact Demon Eyes from demons in the Antoran Wastes, but suffer $s2% additional damage from all sources.
AuraDescription_lang: Disguised as an Agent of the All-Seer.Damage taken increased by $s2%.Allows collection of Intact Demon Eyes.
